      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the breakdown. so if it's just about semantic plausibility, how does the actual formal parsing work in a computational sense? like, if a parser is looking at the branching structure, how does it mathematically decide to attach the PP to the VP vs the NP?",
      "source": "evaluator"
